Made By Hario

These are few maps that I've made for the DtK GunGame servers.

Please feel free to use this map however you choose as long as you give credit.
Some textures by Chris528.

For the maps to work, you'll have to download the textures as well from http://www.fpsbanana.com/textures/707 and install them as directed on Chris's page.

If you're using this map in a server, or just have any feedback, let me know at
flat_gnome@yahoo.com.au

Have fun.
